summary: Big Spoilers for the Clone Saga, although I’m p sure everyone knows about this by now. I’m about to start Revelations Part 3 and...
body:
Big Spoilers for the Clone Saga, although I’m p sure everyone knows about this by now.

I’m about to start Revelations Part 3 and I… want… the Clone Saga to end but I don’t… want… Ben to die. Or baby May. I don’t want to keep reading. 

Also, points to literally everyone, who let me know about their deaths and Norman’s return but kept me in the dark about what the hell’s up with that meeting at the Bugle.

summary: While I love Peter swearing (no one could convince me that when the Juggernaut left Madame Web to die he didn’t say “That...
body: While I love Peter swearing (no one could convince me that when the Juggernaut left Madame Web to die he didn’t say “That fuck!”), I have an equally important place in my heart for him replacing “shit” with “web fluid” in normal idioms, such as “get shit from”.
